<p><span class="anchor" id="p4"></span><span class="c5">واليسير:</span> القليل.<span class="c5"> قَال اللّاه تعالى:</span><a href="#p4" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p5"></span>ذالِكَ كَيْلٌ يَسِيرٌ <span class="c2">«٢»</span>.<a href="#p5" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
