<p><span class="anchor" id="p8"></span><span class="c4">[اليُسرى]</span>: خلاف اليمنى.<a href="#p8" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p9"></span><span class="c5">واليُسرى:</span> نقيض العُسرى.<span class="c5"> قال اللّاه تعالى:</span> فَسَنُيَسِّرُهُ لِلْيُسْرى <span class="c2">«٣»</span>.<a href="#p9" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
